title: Face Blur | Kdenlive VS Adobe Premiere Pro

media:group.media:title: Face Blur | Kdenlive VS Adobe Premiere Pro
media:group.media:description:
This video shows the process of blurring out a face in Kdenlive and Adobe's Premiere Pro side by side. 

Kdenlive is 100% free and open source software that runs on Windows, Linux, and Mac.

Adobe Premiere Pro is a heavily marketed proprietary software that runs on Windows and Mac.

Both are professorial level programs and achieved a similar looking blur in a comparable amount of time.
